Cook pasta as directed on package in large saucepan, adding broccoli during last 5 minutes of cooking time; drain. Cook and stir garlic and chicken breast strips in butter in same saucepan on medium heat 1 to 2 minutes or until garlic is tender but not brown and chicken is heated through. Add pasta and broccoli; toss lightly. Sprinkle with cheese; toss to coat. Serve immediately.